      • YieldNode

        public YieldNode(ISourcePosition position,
         Node argsNode,
         boolean expandedArguments)
        Construct a new YieldNode.
        Parameters:
        position - position of the node in the source
        argsNode - the arguments to the yield
        expandedArguments - whether the arguments should be treated as directly-passed args as in yield 1, 2, 3 (expandedArguments = true) versus yield [1, 2, 3] (expandedArguments = false).
